                      </desc>
                      </item>
                      <item xml:id="a2">
                      <desc>
                      <locus target="#12v" facs="015"> f. 12v, upper margin</locus>: <q>“When the official or the king becomes angry with you, recite Psalm 19 over oil and anoint your face.”</q>
                      </desc>
                      </item>
                      <item xml:id="a3">
                      <desc>
                      <locus target="#74v" facs="077"/>: <q>“When a husband and wife disagree, recite (this psalm, 118) over butter and anoint your body.”</q>
                      </desc>
                      </item>
